You're making me uncomfortable.

362
00:29:00,905 --> 00:29:02,323
Ms. Choi.

363
00:29:03,366 --> 00:29:06,703
I look forward to your
collaboration with Mr. Cha.

364
00:29:06,786 --> 00:29:09,164
