Why does she have to be pretty, too?

438
00:33:47,859 --> 00:33:50,445
If it were up to me,
I'd split them up immediately.

439
00:33:51,946 --> 00:33:52,905
Split who up?

440
00:33:52,989 --> 00:33:54,449
-Choi--
-Choi Da-in.

441
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,538
Director Gold, are you going home?

442
00:34:03,166 --> 00:34:05,460
Am I the only one going home?

443
00:34:07,754 --> 00:34:08,963
Ms. Yu.

444
00:34:09,172 --> 00:34:10,840
Yu-seop, Hyo-jin.

445
00:34:11,007 --> 00:34:14,343
Is there work that you must finish today?

446
00:34:15,511 --> 00:34:17,263
About Mr. Ahn's work...

447
00:34:19,724 --> 00:34:20,933
The insurance...

448
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,190
I can just do it tomorrow.

449
00:34:27,857 --> 00:34:30,151
There's no need to do it today.

450
00:34:33,071 --> 00:34:36,074
Then shall we all call it a day?

451
00:34:36,157 --> 00:34:38,284
Good job today, everyone.

452
00:34:40,203 --> 00:34:41,454
Good job.

453
00:34:51,756 --> 00:34:54,092
What? Do I look too pretty?

454
00:34:55,426 --> 00:34:58,262
I was thinking about what to eat today.

455
00:34:59,013 --> 00:35:00,473
I'm not hungry.

456
00:35:00,681 --> 00:35:02,475
-I doubt that.
-I mean it.

457
00:35:02,558 --> 00:35:04,352
We're going on a drive today.

458
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:06,354
That sounds good. Where to?

459
00:35:07,647 --> 00:35:09,857
I'll take you to my car. Follow me.

