who's really familiar with this place.

470
00:35:56,404 --> 00:35:58,322
Why would I have to listen to this?

471
00:35:58,781 --> 00:36:00,116
You should do it instead.

472
00:36:00,449 --> 00:36:01,284
Me?

473
00:36:01,951 --> 00:36:02,994
Okay, then.

474
00:36:03,828 --> 00:36:05,788
-What is that?
-A building?

475
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:40,406
Part two of Sung Duk-mi's
Seoul Night View Tour.

476
00:36:40,781 --> 00:36:41,908
What was part one?

477
00:36:41,991 --> 00:36:44,118
I already did it. Sung Duk-mi's Penthouse.

478
00:36:47,747 --> 00:36:51,334
